## 🎯 **Documentation Projects**

### **Software Project Documentation**
Structure your project docs for optimal navigation:

```
project/
├── README.md              # Main project overview
├── docs/
│   ├── index.md           # Documentation hub
│   ├── getting-started.md # Quick start guide
│   ├── api/
│   │   ├── index.md       # API documentation index
│   │   ├── authentication.md
│   │   └── endpoints.md
│   ├── tutorials/
│   │   ├── index.md       # Tutorial listing
│   │   ├── basic-usage.md
│   │   └── advanced-features.md
│   └── deployment/
│       ├── index.md       # Deployment guide
│       ├── docker.md
│       └── kubernetes.md
```

**Navigation Features:**
- ✅ Automatic subdirectory linking in footer
- ✅ Local file menus in headers  
- ✅ Breadcrumb navigation between levels
- ✅ Generate comprehensive indexes with `Tools → Generate Index`

